As Valentine approaches, so also does worry for the perfect gift. Looking for something thoughtful as well as beautiful for your significant other or family and friends? Well, here is one cute recipe to help with that thought. Valentine chocolate covered strawberries are easy to make sends the right message and to top all, rides on a low budget. Be sure to give it a try. Notice that all colours of ingredients used are colours that scream ‘Valentine’, thus the addition of it to its name. In no time, your perfect gift, well packed in a cookie box is ready.